Flora of Virginia
*Galax urceolata* (Poir.) Brum.
Trimble Mtn., Augusta Co.

Colony of scores, almost all sterile, on
both sides of Trimble Mtn. Trail on N slope
near ridgrecrest in oak-mixed hardwoods, with
*Gaultheria*, *Kalmia* & *Pieris* & just below
*Xerophyllum* colony. Found by Jacob Kagey &
(Stokesville Quad.) el. 2400 ft. Alvin Dove.
July 8, 1995
Charles E. Stevens with Jacob Kagey & Alvin Dove
No. 24,946
